Our room (and the rest of the hotel) was beautifully decorated and spotlessly clean, with shuttered windows opening onto a pretty, quiet canal.	The room was just lovely, very clean although small, it was tastefully decorated and had a lovely terrace.	The room was a standard double so no view over the canal but the room itself and the bathroom were both really big and well equipped, although no coffee or tea in the room.	Our room did not have a canal view, but was a good size and clean, with a nice clean and quite spacious bathroom.